@StoreManagement.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000
@token = 

### Login to get token
# @name login
POST {{StoreManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Users - sort by id asc
GET {{StoreManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/users?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=id
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Users - sort by username desc
GET {{StoreManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/users?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=username&sortDesc=true
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Products - sort by id desc
GET {{StoreManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/products?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=id&sortDesc=true
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Products - sort by name asc with search
GET {{StoreManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/products?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&searchTerm=milk&sortBy=name
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Categories - sort by id asc
GET {{StoreManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/categories?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=id
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Suppliers - sort by name desc
GET {{StoreManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/suppliers?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=name&sortDesc=true
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Inventory - sort by id asc
GET {{StoreManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/inventory?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=id
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Inventory - filter by productId and sort by quantity desc
GET {{StoreManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/inventory?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&productId=1&sortBy=quantity&sortDesc=true
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Customers - sort by id asc
GET {{StoreManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/customer?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=id
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Customers - search and sort by name desc
GET {{StoreManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/customer?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&searchTerm=john&sortBy=name&sortDesc=true
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Promotions - sort by id asc
GET {{StoreManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/promotion?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=id
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Promotions - sort by startDate desc
GET {{StoreManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/promotion?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=startDate&sortDesc=true
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

